PN,34205
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F342A1673045701
OL,6,F"We have more public support for this
OL,7,Fcampaign to save Radio Foyle than any
OL,8,Fother region," he added.
OL,10,FFormer BBC Radio Foyle presenter Joe
OL,11,FMahon said the station was set up to
OL,12,Freflect life in an area that "was
OL,13,Fculturally and geographically distinct"
OL,14,Fand was considered under served by the
OL,15,FBBC at that time.
OL,3,CLocals voice opposition to BBC Radio
OL,4,CFoyle cuts at public meeting
