PN,34206
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F342A1673045701
OL,6,F"I would like to know when that
OL,7,Fidentity has been seen as less strong?
OL,8,FIt has been strengthened. The decisions
OL,9,Fthat are being made about something as
OL,10,Fculturally and politically important
OL,11,Fare ridiculous," he said.
OL,13,FThe NUJ says it will present
OL,14,Falternative proposals to BBC management
OL,15,Fnext week.
